Package org.neo4j.kernel.impl.index.schema.fusion

Class FusionIndexBase<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.neo4j.kernel.impl.index.schema.fusion.FusionIndexBase<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - type of instances
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    FusionIndexAccessor, FusionIndexPopulator, FusionIndexReader, FusionIndexUpdater
    public abstract class FusionIndexBase<T>
extends Object
    Acting as a simplifier for the multiplexing that is going in inside a fusion index. A fusion index consists of multiple parts, each handling one or more value groups. Each instance, be it a reader, populator or accessor should extend this class to get that multiplexing at a low cost. All parts will live in an array with specific slot constants to each specific part.
